# Sri Asha Forgings - Cloudflare Pages Optimized Redirects
# Standardizing for Clean Extensionless URLs

# 1. Core Pages - Letting Cloudflare Native Clean URLs handle basic matching
# Note: Rules like /about /about.html 200 are removed here because 
# Cloudflare Pages handles these automatically without redundancy issues.

# 2. Legacy and Alternate Paths (301 Permanent)
/home / 301
/index / 301

# 3. Clean Mappings for Specific Filenames
# These are needed because the URL slug differs from the filename
/privacy /privacypolicy.html 200
/terms /Terms.html 200
/faqs /Faqs.html 200
/metallurgy-reports /metallurgy.html 301

# 4. Global Site standardized contact link
/contact /#contact 301

# 5. Catch-all for robust 404 handling
/* /404.html 404
